premise_source_doc_sentence: The mixtape 's production was handled by several record producers , including Dr. Dre , Ervin ` EP ' Pope , The Neptunes , Bink , DJ Shake , Nottz , 1500 or Nothin ' , Che Vicious , D.A. Dorman , Cool & Dre , RZA , Stargate , Mike City , Raw Uncut , Denaun Porter , DJ Haze , DJ Green Lantern , and Travis Barker , among others .
